Description: Precision oncology is rapidly evolving with the integration of artificial intelligence, intelligent diagnostics, and vast amounts of data. This session will delve into the transformative power of AI in precision oncology and its pivotal role in propelling drug development into a new era. Attendees will gain insights into how to embrace this revolution, harnessing the synergy of cutting-edge genomic assays, multimodal real-world data, and AI-driven insights to expedite the discovery and development of novel therapeutics.
